<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Website Simple Saya</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4e73df, #1cc88a);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: white;
            color: #4e73df;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #f8f9fc;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <h1>Halo 👋</h1>
        <p>Ini adalah website simple pertama saya di GitHub</p>
        <a href="https://github.com" class="btn">Kunjungi GitHub</a>
    </header>

    <footer>
        <p>© 2026 - Website Simple by Kamu</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
